Package: twscrape
Type: Package
Title: twscrape: Functionality to Collect Data from Twitter API and screen
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Hauke", "Licht", email = "hauke.licht@uzh.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The {twscrape} package implements functionality to extract data from Twitter.
    Specifically, it provides an interface to seemlessly screen-scrape tweet IDs, 
    and it extends {rtweet} functionality.
